          "If you pre-book a rideshare, still keep the taxi queue as a backup plan. Drivers sometimes cancel at the last minute.",
          "In countries with known taxi scams (certain tourist-heavy destinations in Southeast Asia, North Africa, and Southern Europe), app-based rides are almost always the safer and fairer-priced choice."
